ttps%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>戴帽子的猫</u></a>版本。如果您正在寻找经典之作， <a href="https://zdcs.link/aAVwj4?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Vermont%20Teddy%20Bear&amp;short_url=aAVwj4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>佛蒙特泰迪熊</u></a>是每年搜索次数最多的熊。</p><h2 id="quirky-gifts">奇特的礼物</h2><p>说到复古， <a href="https://zdcs.link/aNDZo3?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=turntables&amp;short_url=aNDZo3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>转盘</u></a>又回来了：今年它们的搜索量增加了 50%。今年“小型便携式音箱”的搜索量增加了 75%，我最喜欢的是<a href="https://zdcs.link/QddoEv?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Sonos%20Roam%202&amp;short_url=QddoEv&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>Sonos Roam 2</u></a> 。不出所料， <a href="https://zdcs.link/9g3mEG?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Playstation%20Portal%20Remote&amp;short_url=9g3mEG&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>PlayStation Portal Remote</u></a>今年很受欢迎。乐高永远是最受欢迎的玩具搜索之一——谷歌推荐了这款<a href="https://zdcs.link/avx1Jq?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Tuxedo%20Cat&amp;short_url=avx1Jq&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>燕尾服猫</u></a>套件。使用<a href="https://zdcs.link/aepWX2?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=backpack%20cooler&amp;short_url=aepWX2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>背包冷藏箱</u></a>为您的野餐增添乐趣，该产品的搜索量增加了 60%。</p><h2 id="gifts-for-active-types">适合活跃型的礼物</h2><p><a href="https://zdcs.link/Qp61E0?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Merrell%20hiking%20boots&amp;short_url=Qp61E0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>Merrell 登山鞋</u></a>显然是年度“靴子”，搜索量猛增 165%。它们适合男士和女士，有各种款式。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/QKDWRV?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Yoga%20mats&amp;short_url=QKDWRV&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>瑜伽垫的</u></a>销量每年一月都会激增，因此，送一张瑜伽垫吧。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/9wG1pq?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Walking%20pads&amp;short_url=9wG1pq&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>步行垫</u></a>今年创下了历史新高，当您穿上步行垫时，您可以穿上同样很受欢迎的<a href="https://zdcs.link/QODNe2?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=News&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Nike%20Motiva%20walking%20shoes&amp;short_url=QODNe2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>Nike Motiva 步行鞋</u></a>。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-le